Breakeven Response Rate

Mailing_cost <- 1.41
Margin <- 60

breakeven_response <- Mailing_cost/(Margin * 0.5)
breakeven_response
[1] 0.047

Function to calculate profit

profit_calc<- function(trgt_population_pctg, response_rate, totl_popl=801821 - 38487)
{
  mailing_cost_lr1 <- Mailing_cost * trgt_population_pctg * 22500
  margin_lr1 <- Margin * response_rate * 0.5 * trgt_population_pctg * 22500
  Profit_lr1 <- margin_lr1 - mailing_cost_lr1
  target_pop<- totl_popl * trgt_population_pctg
  mailing_trgt_pop_cost<- target_pop* Mailing_cost
  margin_trgt_pop<- Margin* response_rate * 0.5 * target_pop
  profit_trgt_pop <- margin_trgt_pop - mailing_trgt_pop_cost
  cat(paste("The expected profit (Test set) is $", format(Profit_lr1),
  "\nThe expected profit (Total Population) is $", format(profit_trgt_pop)))
}
